{"tid":2437666,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"5人涉荃灣參與暴動及縱火開審  一被告未上庭官發拘捕令","createTime":"2021-03-08T04:09:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T11:16:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"124ff9b4688a61931d315917f0b97012ea1fb7f9","tid":2437666,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T04:09:31.000Z","msg":"前年10月1日，全港多區爆發反修例衝突。其中有大批示威者在荃灣聚集堵路，並在馬路上縱火，四男一女事後被捕，分別被控參與暴動及縱火罪，案件今於區域法院開審。<br />\n<br />\n5名被告被控於2019年10月1日在荃灣海壩街一帶參與暴動，首被告另被指在同日同地縱火。據悉，第四被告在預審時已不見蹤影，法庭早前已頒下拘捕令。<br />\n<br />\n控方開案陳詞指，2019年10月1日，有逾200名示威者於荃灣海壩街聚集，他們以雜物堵路，破壞現場設施，甚至在街上縱火。於下午3時40分，<strong><span class=\"red\">機動暴隊</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />軍裝警員在大河道面對海霸街方向設置防線，與示威者對峙，期間多次發出警告，更曾發出多枚橡膠子彈，惟示威者沒有散去。<br />\n<br />\n下午約4時，有一名黑衣人靠近警方防線，將可燃液體淋在行人路上，然後點燃，形成一條火線。之後，一名以白布蒙面、手持淺藍色摺傘的首被告上前並一幅狀似橫額的物體拋入火堆之中，現場有片段拍攝到整個縱火過程。期間，示威者不斷向警方投擲硬物及汽油彈，並向警方防線推進。下午4時，警方以快速推進方式衝向示威者，進行驅散行動。示威者四散，而首被告則跑向荃興徑警方防線方向逃走，終被警員制服。餘下3名被告亦在警方推進期間先後被捕。"},{"pid":"c00cec9df44419e91d51ac97137195976da3848b","tid":2437666,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T04:10:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14206\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14206&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058r9EqtgOipuK5hw8%2B6jdv%2Bo%3D&h=2a09198b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14206</a><br />\n<br />\n#區域法院二樓第七庭<br />\n#練錦鴻法官<br />\n#1001荃灣 #審訊 [1/15]<br />\n<br />\n陳, 陳, 李, 郭(19-39)<br />\n控罪：<br />\n1) 暴動 <br />\n2) 縱火 [D1]<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n詳情：<br />\n(1) A1-5同被控於2019年10月1日在荃灣海壩街，與其他不知名人士參與暴動。<br />\n(2) A1被控於同日同地，與其他不知名人士，無合理辯解下用火損壞另一人的財物。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n❌各被告不認罪❌<br />\n<br />\n開案陳詞<br />\n當時大約200人於海壩街設路置，亦有示威者自製盾牌，有示威者手持鐵枝，敲打欄杆以發出敲打聲音，不斷向警方防線作出推進，警方向海壩街發出催淚彈但事威者沒有後退，後來示威者意圖再推進，故警方發出橡膠子彈以作驅趕。<br />\n<br />\nD1 陳<br />\n由警方拍攝影像看見D1在地上畫成一條火線，手穿黑褲白鞋黑衫，手持藍色縮骨遮，面上蓋住白色面布。警方的證據亦拍攝到D1當時與其他人示威者在一起的畫面，並畫成火線的畫面。<br />\n<br />\n後來警方推進荃興徑，警方看見4-5名人士於荃興徑，警員20374於金坊美食門外拘補D1，其後以非法集結將其拘捕。在其身上搜出黑藍色手套，綠黑色打火機、一張電話卡、一張SD卡、一條白色毛巾。<br />\n<br />\nD2 陳<br />\n當時身穿白頭盔、粉紅色頭盔、游泳鏡、灰背囊。在其背囊發現1000ml生理鹽水、黑手袖、一張長者八達通、一張八達通、四枝10ml消毒藥水、一件黑色圓領tshirt及一張電話卡，其後以非法集結將其拘捕。<br />\n<br />\nD3 李<br />\n於啟智街及海壩街交界被捕，被捕時穿著黑衫黑波鞋，面戴防毒面具，其後以非法集結將其拘捕。<br />\n<br />\nD5 郭<br />\n在啟智街及海壩街交界被捕，面戴灰/粉紅色防毒面具及黑色書包，在其身上搜獲身上有一頂黑色漁夫帽、一個3M眼罩、深藍色外套、一張sim card、一張八達通，並現發袋中有一枝以透明密實袋內藏有紅色「東元牌」聚氨酯泡沫填縫劑。警員發現上述物品，其後以非法集結將其拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n其後示威者後退以消防車後作為防線，但仍然不斷想推進警方防線，故警方徹到大河道並將第二三五被告帶往大河道橋底看守，示威者隨即亦再次霸佔海壩街，1628帶所有被告坐警車前往荃灣警署。<br />\n<br />\n💛感謝臨時直播員💛"},{"pid":"b91dbb6a9ff2b60ae0972df18624a81c1d0469ea","tid":2437666,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T04:10:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d5f036016ea14a6c846237f6d7afb3744e8ec3","tid":2437666,"uid":270307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T04:10:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"274d3987126bde1943d9acef4b6e2418c1a67b06","tid":2437666,"uid":191926,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T04:10:32.000Z","msg":"機動暴隊<br />\n<br />\n個名改得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1482f915c55eeabb81eea1b0e1f61b5662720488","tid":2437666,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T04:11:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5de94920f57a8a434166d965f13dbbaecff6354","tid":2437666,"uid":87985,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T04:25:06.000Z","msg":"希望AP4係走咗<br />\n好人平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a549d383c3a6dd6c13f3f592c9a7b1cb2e0e8798","tid":2437666,"uid":14941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:54:35.000Z","msg":"暴動師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 手足快走"},{"pid":"34b6c13bc7b060f43aa8115b76a6c3d5b9bdf567","tid":2437666,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:19:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b06924dce8fe7702fa932b1c4c4986aea4f4d8","tid":2437666,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:29:36.000Z","msg":"祝生活愉快"},{"pid":"548362bba6f206b3bbe48dfab638f9ee28767ab2","tid":2437666,"uid":288765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:36:51.000Z","msg":"共黨借國安法報返國慶嘅仇"},{"pid":"c8a6f28aa9269f42de37f91394c445682868cd88","tid":2437666,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:42:37.000Z","msg":"外聘檢控官吳美華大律師在傳召證人前，先向法庭傳上一份書面陳述書，即一名警員證人的口供作為證據。惟該陳述書在庭上讀出後，連官隨即指出文中提及「四名示威者」，但沒有提及是誰，質疑稱：「咁好難連埋其他證人黎講。」吳大律師聽罷撤回該口供，決定之後傳召該證人上庭作供。<br />\n<br />\n證人警員文志堅供稱，當日有消息指有數百名示威者在荃灣街市街及海霸街聚集堵路，逐與同僚奉命到青山公路荃灣段眾安街交界掃蕩。於下午3時許到達大河道交界，設立防線。在防線前方約100米，有逾200人聚集，他們以水馬等雜物形成路障，有些人手持鐵支、向警方投擲磚頭及汽油彈。警方先後舉藍旗及黑旗警告，示威者均沒有理會。"},{"pid":"3126e3bb1d2bf599764a693460baa24c0b6761a1","tid":2437666,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:09:49.000Z","msg":"案情指首被告遭拍下縱火過程<br />\n<br />\n媒體拍下兩人行為，他們縱火後仍在海壩街及荃興徑附近的行人路出現。首被告曾拿起一支長形條狀物件，與其他示威者蹲在行人路的垃圾桶旁。下午 4 時，警方向示威者快速推進，示威者隨即逃跑，首被告跑入荃興徑，遭警員制服。穿著黑衫褲、戴頭巾及泳鏡的次被告，在海壩街及路德圍交界行人路被警員制服。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/10-1-%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E6%A1%88-%E5%AE%98%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E8%AD%A6%E5%8F%A3%E4%BE%9B%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E6%9B%B8%E9%9D%A2%E5%91%88%E5%A0%82-%E4%BD%A0%E5%81%9A%E4%B8%BB%E6%8E%A7-%E6%88%91%E5%94%94%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%95%99%E4%BD%A0%E9%BB%9E%E5%81%9A%E5%98%A2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F10-1-%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258F%25A3%25E4%25BE%259B%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2583%25BD%25E6%259B%25B8%25E9%259D%25A2%25E5%2591%2588%25E5%25A0%2582-%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E5%2581%259A%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%258E%25A7-%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%258F%25AF%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%2595%2599%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E9%25BB%259E%25E5%2581%259A%25E5%2598%25A2%2F&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058r9EqtgOipuK5hw8%2B6jdv%2Bo%3D&h=e0008cd8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F10-1-%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258F%25A3%25E4%25BE%259B%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2583%25BD%25E6%259B%25B8%25E9%259D%25A2%25E5%2591%2588%25E5%25A0%2582-%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E5%2581%259A%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%258E%25A7-%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%258F%25AF%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%2595%2599%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E9%25BB%259E%25E5%2581%259A%25E5%2598%25A2%2F&h=ac77689a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/10-1-%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E6%A1%88-%E5%AE%98%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E8%AD%A6%E5%8F%A3%E4%BE%9B%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E6%9B%B8%E9%9D%A2%E5%91%88%E5%A0%82-%E4%BD%A0%E5%81%9A%E4%B8%BB%E6%8E%A7-%E6%88%91%E5%94%94%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%95%99%E4%BD%A0%E9%BB%9E%E5%81%9A%E5%98%A2/</a>"},{"pid":"2adc16028bb8f5ada35fe7d07b09734a32ededdb","tid":2437666,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:31:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3cc68ae06155441af6567616e74134a4b00065d","tid":2437666,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:43:48.000Z","msg":"18歲中五生「健仔」曾志健前年10月1日在荃灣遭警員實彈射傷，連同六名男女被警方拘控暴動罪，其中四人今就暴動及縱火罪受審。控方案情指警方當天出動催淚彈和橡膠子彈驅散示威者，拘捕案中被告後，示威者重新集結施襲，警方需帶著被告撤退，有便衣警擎槍戒備。控方起初打算不傳召小隊副指揮官上庭，僅宣讀其供詞，惟法官練錦鴻指口供疑有缺漏，「我唔可以教你點做嘢，我只提出有少少連貫性問題」，控方遂撤回口供，稍後傳召該證人上庭。<br />\n<br />\n控方在庭上讀出機動部隊A連小隊副指揮官高級督察陳文傑的口供，口供稱同袍當時拘捕四名示威者。法官練錦鴻質疑口供沒有提及該四名示威者的身份，控方回應稱有證供指四名示威者為次被告、第三、第四及第五被告。<br />\n<br />\n辯方則指，次被告並非示威者，亦認為該份口供未能連結第五被告。法官練錦鴻稱「我只提出有少少連貫性問題」，又稱「你做主控，我做仲裁，你有資料我就考慮，我唔可以教你點做嘢」。控方留意到練官的「關注」，撤回該份口供，稍後傳召該小隊副指揮官上庭。<br />\n<br />\n控方開案陳詞稱，前年十月一日大批示威者在荃灣區內集結，燃燒雜物，破壞道路設施，用雜物堵塞馬路。警方新界南機動部隊成員奉命到場，此時有逾200名示威者在海壩街及啟志街築起防線，匿於水馬及「傘陣」後與警方對峙，大部份示威者穿上黑衣，戴頭盔，穿上保護裝備，亦備有自製盾牌、棒狀物及防毒口罩。他們敲打欄杆、燈柱等，揮動鐵枝，向警方投擲磚塊及汽油彈。警方警告要求示威者離開，否則發射催淚彈及橡膠子彈，惟示威者沒有散去。警方施放催淚彈及發射橡膠子彈。<br />\n<br />\n針對首被告的縱火罪，控方指同日下午約四時，有身穿黑衣、手持深色下雨傘的示威者從其防線左邊的海壩街行人路朝警方防線走去，將可疑液體淋在行人路上，點燃液體，造成一條火線，橫跨雙方防線間的行人路。首被告當時身穿黑衣黑褲及白鞋，用白布包面，手持一把與別不同的淺藍色摺傘，將一幅狀似橫額的物品投向火堆，之前設火線的示威者再把燈箱踢進火堆，然後兩人雙雙返回示威者防線。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210308/TJFN646ALZGQHGABCISEMKWTM4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210308%2FTJFN646ALZGQHGABCISEMKWTM4%2F&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058r9EqtgOipuK5hw8%2B6jdv%2Bo%3D&h=03463a9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210308%2FTJFN646ALZGQHGABCISEMKWTM4%2F&h=f808bbb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210308/TJFN646ALZGQHGABCISEMKWTM4/</a>"},{"pid":"0c2fba572ac48f7a170fb55434d233986d161744","tid":2437666,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:53:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"babc6f03ef4075ff86ad4e21e6f325b54b2f9266","tid":2437666,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T08:32:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49309967caccd997a0188e0d11f75f124aaa5a5d","tid":2437666,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:03:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfcf1f72eacdaecb72dc2ce5151c522845124823","tid":2437666,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:06:02.000Z","msg":"無上庭既係健仔？"},{"pid":"a70ea3d7d14d2fdfc381034ee9cb7f7b68862d8c","tid":2437666,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:06:47.000Z","msg":"練狗屌你老母"},{"pid":"a35243c69b5c492d378f9d0c6beca3cd663df550","tid":2437666,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfcf1f72eacdaecb72dc2ce5151c522845124823","tid":2437666,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:06:02.000Z","msg":"無上庭既係健仔？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:08:38.000Z","msg":"另一個被告"},{"pid":"3eab9cdf74aba30f298a4106904b9a8180c19d64","tid":2437666,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfcf1f72eacdaecb72dc2ce5151c522845124823","tid":2437666,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":